net.minecraftforge.fml.common

接口 IEntitySelectorFactory


  • public interface IEntitySelectorFactory
    Allows mods to create custom selectors in commands. Registered in GameRegistry.registerEntitySelector(IEntitySelectorFactory, String...) For an example implementation, see CustomEntitySelectorTest

    • 方法概要

      Called every time a command that contains entity selectors is executed

    • 方法详细资料

      • createPredicates

        @Nonnull
java.util.List<com.google.common.base.Predicate<Entity>> createPredicates(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> arguments,
                                                                                    java.lang.String mainSelector,
                                                                                    ICommandSender sender,
                                                                                    Vec3d position)
        Called every time a command that contains entity selectors is executed
        参数:
        arguments - A map with all arguments and their values
        mainSelector - The main selector string (e.g. 'a' for all players or 'e' for all entities)
        sender - The sender of the command
        position - A position either specified in the selector arguments or by the players position. See EntitySelector.getPosFromArguments(Map, Vec3d)
        返回:
        A list of new predicates, can be empty (Collections.emptyList() but not null.
